    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This specimen features the iconic S54B32 atmospheric straight-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a precision-calibrated Double VANOS system. The chassis is structurally flawless, with zero subframe stress fractures and a completely documented service history. Power is managed by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component is in peak operating condition, ensuring the visceral, communicative handling this platform is renowned for. Finished in concours-level paint with an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a turnkey example for the most discerning purist.",
