      "description": "This vehicle is the definition of showroom quality, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every tactile surface feels as crisp as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, with a comprehensive service history and every feature functioning in perfect harmony. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a truly flawless example that requires nothing but a new home.",
